# Launchpad Contract Overview

The Launchpad contract enables a time-limited token sale on the Alephium blockchain with the following key features:

- Whitelist-controlled participant access  
- Hard cap on total funds raised  
- Minimum and maximum contribution limits per address  
- Immediate token distribution upon contribution  
- Emergency pause/unpause functionality for owner  
- Owner-controlled token price updates  
- Secure withdrawal of funds by the owner after sale completion  

This contract is designed for projects looking to raise funds securely and transparently while protecting investors.
